Title: Determinant Representations for Correlation Functions of Spin-1/2 XXX  and XXZ Heisenberg Magnets
Authors: F. H. L. Essler and H. Frahm and A. G. Izergin and V. E. Korepin
Abstract: We consider correlation functions of the spin-$\half$ XXX and XXZ Heisenberg chains in a magnetic field. Starting from the algebraic Bethe Ansatz we derive representations for various correlation functions in terms of determinants of Fredholm integral operators.
